To scale images(used for training set):
scaleImages(sourcePath, destinationPath, scale)
e.g. scaleImages('TrainImages', 'TrainImagesScaled', 1/2.5);

To train an adaBoost linear classifier:
[strongClassifier, subWindowSize] = trainAdaBoost(sourcePath);
e.g. [strongClassifier, subWindowSize] = trainAdaBoost('TrainImagesScaled');

To test an adaBoost linear classifier:
- for a file:
positiveSubWindows = testAdaBoost('D:\Matlab_Projects\LG\adaBoost\dataset\TrainImages\pos-0.pgm', strongClassifier, subWindowSize);

- for all files in a directory:
positiveSubWindows = testAdaBoost('D:\Matlab_Projects\LG\adaBoost\dataset\TrainImages', strongClassifier, subWindowSize);
